This exception does not alter the terms of those third-party licenses.

4. No Implied Endorsement

Use of the official binaries for commercial purposes does not imply
any endorsement, sponsorship, or affiliation by the copyright holder,
unless explicitly stated in writing.

5. Reservation of Rights

All rights not expressly granted by this exception are reserved by
the copyright holder.
